lead_paragraph: With leading scorer and rebounder Sindarius Thornwell out indefinitely, No. 20 South Carolina turned to Duane Notice and P.J. Dozier to fill the void on Sunday.

headline.print_headline: Notice, Dozier Lead No. 20 South Carolina Past FIU, 70-54
